   <ul>
   <li><a href="#ArgBasPriResForAutLibNotSelOwn">2.1 Arguments Based on the Principle of Respect for Autonomy, on Libertarianism, or on a notion of Self-Ownership</a></li>
   <li><a href="#SavLiv">2.2 The Saving of Lives</a></li>
   <li><a href="#Con">2.3 Consistency</a></li>
   </ul></li>
<li><a href="#HarRis">3. Harm and Risk</a></li>
<li><a href="#Alt">4. Altruism</a>
   <ul>
   <li><a href="#AltAlwGooThi">4.1 Is altruism (always) a good thing?</a></li>
   <li><a href="#WouOrgSalDisRedAlt">4.2 Would organ sale displace or reduce altruism?</a></li>
   <li><a href="#AltSupDutRes">4.3 Altruism, Supererogation, and Duties to Rescue</a></li>
